latestIgtvVideos.title: Style - #Stolehisblazer oops !
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Quarantine and play dress up.

Using my Husbands blazer that he got custom made for our 1 year Anniversary. 
Look 1 - Blazer - Paresh Lamba, Dress - Bcbgmaxazria, Boots - Top shop. 
Look 2 - Blazer - Paresh Lamba, Jeans - Zara, Bikini tube - Shein, Shoes - Shein. 
Look 3 - Blazer - Paresh Lamba, Top - Bershka, Skirt - Zara, Shoes - Trufflecollection/Myntra. 
@pareshlambasignatures @zara @topshop @bershkacollection  @sheinofficial  @bcbgmaxazria 
P.S - Hope everyone’s safe and doing well 🙏🏻♥️ Take this time to slow down, take a step back and realise how we really impact the earth and one another. That we aren’t in full control as we think we are. We are all connected 🌏 And we will get through this together 🤗 
Few things I’ve been doing while in this Quarantine period - 
1 : Spending a great amount of family time/Husband time. 
2 : Cooking with my partner has been one of the most FUN things ever. 
3 : Binge watching on Netflix. 
4 : Cleaning 🙈 Yup ! Cleaning out all the unwanted/unnecessary clutter. 
5 : Spending a few minutes every night before bed to pray for those in need and those warriors helping the ones in need. 
And lastly, 
6 : My most favourite part 🙆🏻‍♀️ Any guesses ? .. . *hint* This Video probably says it all ! 🐽

Kayyyy now byeeeeeeee 🙋🏻‍♀️ Be good or don’t 😂 But stay safe ♥️ Song/music - Beautiful tonight - Yves v & Seven. @yves_v @sevenn
